data.description: Perfect location and the newest home in Germantown area built in 2001. This home was recently updated with new appliances, new carpet, and renewed hardwood floor in living room. A separate laundry room includes washer and dryer. This home features three bedrooms with the master suite and a full bath on the first floor, two additional bedrooms with full bath on second floor. It has off street parking and privacy fence enclosed back yard. Low maintenance exterior
